&lt;li&gt;Install, configure &amp;amp; manage print queues.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Troubleshoot DNS, DHCP and TCP/IP issues.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience administering Windows 10/11 and Server 2012 and above.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience administering Windows Server 2012 and above.&lt;/li&gt;
