&lt;li&gt;Experience working in Financial services and/or MSP space.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Microsoft certified.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to work through issues methodically.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Basic experience with policy management (Group Policy &amp;amp; Intune).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in support Mac OS X devices.&lt;/li&gt;
