&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in IT support, system administration, or a client-facing technical role preferred&lt;br&gt;• Hands-on experience building and configuring Windows PCs&lt;br&gt;• Basic understanding of:&lt;/li&gt;
