&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Summary:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As our Contracts Manager, you&#39;ll drive end-to-end contract operations by drafting, negotiating, and managing customer, vendor, and partner agreements with precision, scalability, and legal compliance. You&#39;ll collaborate cross-functionally to optimize workflows, centralize and prioritize work withing our Legal Operations group, lay the foundations for a CLM system, and enhance the efficiency of our Contract lifecycle.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities (including, but not limited to):&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Administer Customer Contracts&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
