&lt;li&gt;Administer 401(k) plan including eligibility, enrollments, and contributions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate annual compliance testing including ADP, ACP, and Top-Heavy testing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage 401(k) vendor relationship with Fidelity or other provider&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Process loan and distribution requests in compliance with plan documents&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support plan audits and Form 5500 filing preparation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure accurate

